name: Cutlist
body:
# What does it do?
CutList plugin for Sketchup takes your model and produces a list of all selected components/groups and their dimensions helping you determine how much of each material you need to produce your design. It also has capabilities to layout these materials on stock sizes of material.

# Notes

* Since 15 Jan 2014, Google does not allow downloads to be stored at their site (general Google decision for this site, nothing to do with this particular project)

* v4.1.10 is the current latest version, uploaded on 14 Jan 2014 still available from the Google code site [Latest version on Google code](https://code.google.com/p/cutlist/downloads/detail?name=sr_cutlist_v4.1.10.rbz)
